text.#text:
The Roadless
			 Area Conservation Rule established under part 294 of title 36, Code of Federal
			 Regulations (and successor regulations), does not apply with respect to any
			 National Forest System land in the State of Alaska.

current-chamber.#text: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

official-title.#text:
To exempt National Forest System land in the State of
		  Alaska from the Roadless Area Conservation Rule.
